    "実施履歴": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "History"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "このマーカーを削除": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Delete this marker"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "完了": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Done"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "通知を設定できません": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Can’t set notification"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "通知が許可されていません。設定アプリ →「PestMap」→「通知」で許可してください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Notifications aren’t allowed. Enable them in Settings → “PestMap” → “Notifications.”"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "過去の日時には設定できません。未来の日時を選んでください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You can’t choose a past time. Please pick a future date and time."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "通知の登録に失敗しました。時間をおいて再度お試しください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Failed to schedule the notification. Please try again later."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ブラックキャップ": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Bait Trap"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "スプレー": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Spray"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "くん煙剤": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fumigant"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "その他": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Other"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "指定なし": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "None"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ゴキブリ": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cockroaches"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "アリ": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ants"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "蚊": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mosquitoes"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ダニ": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mites"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "繰り返さない": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Don’t repeat"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "毎月": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Every month"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "3ヶ月ごと": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Every 3 months"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "半年ごと": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Every 6 months"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "毎年": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Every year"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "リマインドはありません": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No reminders"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "マーカーに次回の予定を設定すると、ここに一覧表示されます": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Set a next date on a marker and it will appear here."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "予定 %lld 件": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%lld reminders"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "予定 %lld 件 ・ 期限切れ %lld 件": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%lld reminders · %lld overdue"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "期限切れ": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Overdue"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "通知がオフです。タップして設定で許可してください。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Notifications are off. Tap to allow them in Settings."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "閉じる": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Close"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "季節の害虫対策アドバイス": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Seasonal pest control tips"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "春・梅雨・夏・秋の年4回、その季節に効く害虫対策のヒントを通知でお届けします。アプリを開かなくても対策のタイミングを逃しません。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Get pest-control tips four times a year (spring, rainy season, summer, autumn). You won’t miss the right timing even without opening the app."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "害虫対策のリマインド": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pest control reminder"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "春の害虫対策": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Spring pest control"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "梅雨の害虫対策": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Rainy-season pest control"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "夏の害虫対策": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Summer pest control"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "秋の害虫対策": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Autumn pest control"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "気温が上がりゴキブリが活動を始める季節です。ブラックキャップの設置・交換の好機です。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "As it warms up, cockroaches become active — a good time to place or replace bait traps."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "湿気でダニ・カビが増えやすい時期。除湿・換気とダニ対策を見直しましょう。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Humidity helps mites and mold thrive. Review dehumidifying, ventilation, and mite control."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "蚊やゴキブリが最盛期。設置済みの対策の効き目を確認しましょう。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Mosquitoes and cockroaches peak now. Check that your existing measures still work."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "越冬前のこの時期の駆除が効果的。来春の発生を抑えられます。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Treating now, before overwintering, is effective and curbs next spring’s outbreak."
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "version": "1.0"
}